<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>PAN Card Application Process | DocAssist</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/aadhar.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css">
</head>
<body>
    <header class="doc-header">
        <div class="container">
            <h1>PAN Card Documentation</h1>
            <p>Permanent Account Number by the Income Tax Department</p>
        </div>
    </header>

    <main class="container">
        <section class="doc-overview">
            <div class="card">
                <img src="/images/<%= data.image_data %>" alt="Aadhaar Logo" class="doc-logo">
                <div class="doc-meta">
                    <p><strong>Issuing Authority:</strong> Income Tax Department, Government of India</p>
                    <p><strong>Purpose:</strong> Identification for tax and financial transactions</p>
                    <p><strong>Validity:</strong> Lifetime</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="application-process">
            <h2><i class="fas fa-list-ol"></i> Step-by-Step Application Process</h2>
            
            <div class="process-steps">
                <div class="step">
                    <div class="step-number">1</div>
                    <div class="step-content">
                        <h3>Choose Application Method</h3>
                        <p>Apply through either:</p>
                        <ul>
                            <li><strong>Online:</strong> Via NSDL (<a href="https://www.onlineservices.nsdl.com/paam/endUserRegisterContact.html" target="_blank">www.tin-nsdl.com</a>) or UTIITSL (<a href="https://www.pan.utiitsl.com/PAN/" target="_blank">www.pan.utiitsl.com</a>)</li>
                            <li><strong>Offline:</strong> Through PAN service centers or authorized agents</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="step">
                    <div class="step-number">2</div>
                    <div class="step-content">
                        <h3>Fill Application Form</h3>
                        <p>Complete Form 49A (for Indian citizens) or Form 49AA (for foreigners):</p>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Provide personal details (name, DOB, address)</li>
                            <li>Select document proofs for identity, address, and DOB</li>
                            <li>Mention source of income (if applicable)</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="step">
                    <div class="step-number">3</div>
                    <div class="step-content">
                        <h3>Submit Documents</h3>
                        <p>Attach scanned copies (for online) or photocopies (for offline) of:</p>
                        <ul>
                            <li><strong>Proof of Identity:</strong> Aadhaar, Passport, Voter ID, Driving License</li>
                            <li><strong>Proof of Address:</strong> Aadhaar, Utility bills, Bank statement</li>
                            <li><strong>Proof of Date of Birth:</strong> Birth certificate, School leaving certificate</li>
                            <li><strong>Passport-size photograph</strong> (for offline applications)</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="step">
                    <div class="step-number">4</div>
                    <div class="step-content">
                        <h3>Payment of Fees</h3>
                        <p>Pay the application fee (excluding GST):</p>
                        <ul>
                            <li>₹93 (Indian communication address)</li>
                            <li>₹864 (Foreign communication address)</li>
                            <li>Payment methods: Credit/Debit card, Net Banking, Demand Draft</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="step">
                    <div class="step-number">5</div>
                    <div class="step-content">
                        <h3>Verification Process</h3>
                        <p>For online applications:</p>
                        <ul>
                            <li>e-KYC through Aadhaar OTP (instant e-PAN)</li>
                            <li>Or submit physical documents at nearest PAN center within 15 days</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="step">
                    <div class="step-number">6</div>
                    <div class="step-content">
                        <h3>Receive PAN Card</h3>
                        <p>Delivery timeline:</p>
                        <ul>
                            <li><strong>e-PAN:</strong> Instant for Aadhaar-based applications</li>
                            <li><strong>Physical card:</strong> 15-20 working days via India Post</li>
                            <li>Track status using acknowledgment number</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="video-guide">
            <h2><i class="fas fa-video"></i> PAN Card Application Tutorial</h2>
            <div class="video-container">
                <iframe width="560" height="315" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/p1elAk8tD8k" title="How to Apply for PAN Card Online" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>            </div>
            <p class="video-caption">How to apply for a PAN card online - step-by-step video guide</p>
        </section>

        <section class="important-notes">
            <h2><i class="fas fa-exclamation-circle"></i> Important Information</h2>
            <div class="notes-grid">
                <div class="note-card">
                    <h3><i class="fas fa-rupee-sign"></i> Application Fee</h3>
                    <p>₹93 + GST for applicants with an Indian address, ₹864 + GST for foreign address.</p>                </div>
                <div class="note-card">
                    <h3><i class="fas fa-users"></i> For Minors</h3>
                    <p>PAN can be issued for minors using guardian's documents. Update required after 18 years of age.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="note-card">
                    <h3><i class="fas fa-sync-alt"></i> Corrections/Updates</h3>
                    <p>PAN correction/update requests can be made online with supporting documents. Fee: ₹96 (approx).</p>
                </div>
                <div class="note-card">
                    <h3><i class="fas fa-phone-alt"></i> Helpline</h3>
                    <p>NSDL Helpdesk: <strong>020-27218080</strong><br>
                    UTIITSL Helpdesk: <strong>1800 22 0306</strong><br>
                    Email: <a href="mailto:tininfo@nsdl.co.in">tininfo@nsdl.co.in</a></p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
        <section class="faq-section">
            <h2><i class="fas fa-question-circle"></i> Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
            <div class="faq-item">
                <h3>Can I apply for PAN card without Aadhaar?</h3>
                <p>Yes, but Aadhaar-based applications are processed faster. Other valid documents can be used as alternatives.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="faq-item">
                <h3>What is the difference between PAN and TAN?</h3>
                <p>PAN is for individuals/entities, while TAN (Tax Deduction Account Number) is required for entities that deduct tax at source.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="faq-item">
                <h3>How long is PAN card valid?</h3>
                <p>PAN card has lifetime validity and doesn't require renewal.</p>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>

